00:47:31.380 --> 00:47:38.490
But he was warning against
the danger of [inaudible]

00:47:38.490 --> 00:47:44.090
and how might upset
the American democracy.

00:47:44.090 --> 00:47:50.170
And Lincoln's words
echo through the ages.

